Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Say}Nè, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You say you're not nice to me, but aren't you the one making my bentos?}Em nói em không tốt với anh, nhưng không phải chính em làm bentou cho anh hay sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Believe me, that makes me glad.}Chuyện đó làm anh rất vui đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Thanks a lot.}Cảm ơn em nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:28.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{Oh no...}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{He's rubbing your head!}Anh ấy đang rờ đầu cậu kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, it's really not what you think.}Dù gì thì cũng không phải những gì em nghĩ đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Come on, I'll carry you.}Thôi nào, để anh giúp em.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Straighten up a little bit.}Leo lên đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{He's...}Anh ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong}Sao thế, Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Nothing.}Không có gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I'm finally here}Cháu tới rồi đây, Nanami-schwan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Where are you? Where are you hiding?}Cô ở đâu? Cô trốn chốn nào thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Over there?}Kia ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanami-saan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Dumb Onii?!}Baka Onii?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{What are you doing here?}Em làm cái quái gì ở đây thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Why are}Tại sao {\i1}{you}anh{\i0} {here}lại ở đây?!{ Where's} Yuuya-senpai đâu rồi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I don't know!}Biết chết liền!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Don't look, Baldspot!}Đừng có nhìn, đồ hói đầu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I'm not balding!}Anh mày không hói nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{This is pretty hard!}Khó quá đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{There!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Cheer up already! You ended\N up filling the gauge!}Vui lên đi nào! Hên là cậu làm đầy lại máy đo đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{You sure take things in stride.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:48.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{Aren't you the least bit suspicious\N after seeing those two?}Cậu không nghi ngờ gì sau khi chứng kiến bọn họ ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Eh? Yeah, well...}A? Bởi vì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan {said nothing happened.}nói không có gì hết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Why wouldn't I trust the man I love?}Làm sao tớ lại không tin người tớ yêu được cơ chứ?
